      • getPlayers

        Players getPlayers(java.lang.String firstName,
                   java.lang.String lastName,
                   java.lang.String position,
                   java.lang.String age)
        path: "/liga/rest/liga/player?fn&ln&p&a" method: GET where: fn is a first name of player ln is a last name of player p is a position of player a is an age of player If first name and last name are not null it returns players who has first name and last name exact as 'fn' and 'ln' If age is not null you will got players who has exact age as 'a' If position is not null you will got players who has exact position as 'p' IF all parameters are null it will return all players
        Parameters:
        firstName - String
        lastName - String
        position - String
        age - Integer
        Returns:
        XmlRootElement called players with elements such as: player - same informations like in player but multiplied

      • getClubs

        Clubs getClubs(java.lang.String name,
               java.lang.String city)
        Get all clubs defined by n and/or c path: "liga/rest/liga/club?n&c" method: GET where: n is a club's name c is a club's city If city and name is not null it will get Clubs (one) which have city and name same as parameters name and city If both parameters are null it will return all clubs

        name - String
        city - String
        Returns:
        XmlRootElement named Clubs which contains: XmlElement Club which have same elements as Club look at /liga/rest/liga/club/{idc}

      • update

        java.lang.String update(Player player)
        Update information about player path /liga/rest/liga/player method: PUT NOTE: IF even after successful update your player did not change relationship club you need to check if club exists in database. send request to /liga/rest/liga/club/{idc} where idc is a Identity of club NOTE 2: Do NOT send any goals objects or assists or club object because it will be overwritten if object is found in database.
        Parameters:
        player - XmlRootElement player which contains same informations as player (look at /liga/rest/liga/player method: POST)
        Returns:
        String whether player was updated or not
